Package: zealhmm
Title: Simulation-Calibrated HMM Ancestry Calling for NILs (Analysis Repo)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Fausto", "Rodriguez Zapata", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "thegemmalab@ncsu.edu")
Description: Analysis and benchmark repository backing the nilHMM methods paper.
    Installs the nilHMM package, runs the ancestry-caller comparison across
    sequencing modalities (Skim WGS, BRB-seq, target-seq) on BZea NILs,
    calibrates and validates caller parameters against Broman simcross
    simulations, and renders the paper's figures and analysis notes. This is
    not itself a library: R/ holds shared analysis helpers and the simcross
    generator, analysis/ holds the rendered notes.
